== In popular culture ==

In 1968 the Michael P. Antoine Company produced the Walt Disney Company musical film &quot;The One and Only, Genuine, Original Family Band&quot; which centers on the election of 1888 and the annexing and subdividing of the Dakota Territory into states (which was a major issue of the election).

